WEBVTT

00:13.600 --> 00:15.320
Look, Paula's markers,

00:15.400 --> 00:17.400
with chewed up caps,
like you used to do.

00:17.480 --> 00:18.720
Thanks, Mom. Give me one.

00:19.960 --> 00:23.800
So, on the day of our first date
I arrived 25 minutes early.

00:23.920 --> 00:25.600
I called him and he said

00:25.680 --> 00:27.600
he was heading out right then.

00:27.680 --> 00:28.600
See you soon.

00:28.680 --> 00:30.040
We met

00:30.840 --> 00:32.160
here, at Hanoi.

00:33.400 --> 00:36.680
He walked there
and it only took five to seven minutes.

00:36.760 --> 00:41.240
Pity, for once you land a good guy...
Why do you want to know how long it took?

00:41.520 --> 00:43.880
To know how far away
from the cafeteria he was.

00:44.440 --> 00:45.400
DISTANCE WALKING 5 TO 7 MINS

00:45.480 --> 00:46.320
500 MTS APPROX.

00:46.400 --> 00:50.280
In that time frame he could have
traveled 500 meters at best.

00:53.200 --> 00:54.280
More or less.

00:56.560 --> 00:58.080
his hideout

00:58.160 --> 00:59.280
is in this area.

00:59.760 --> 01:02.520
He took one of these streets
to get to the cafeteria.

01:02.600 --> 01:04.920
I'm sure one of the surveillance cameras
taped it.

01:05.000 --> 01:07.240
I have to narrow it down.
Give me another one.

01:12.480 --> 01:14.360
I'll get the recordings
from that area

01:14.440 --> 01:16.080
to figure out the route he took.

01:18.640 --> 01:20.560
Are you sure of this?

01:21.120 --> 01:21.960
Mom,

01:23.240 --> 01:25.400
I'll find him no matter what it takes.

01:25.480 --> 01:26.360
Be careful, dear.

01:57.280 --> 01:58.760
We have a badly injured man.

01:58.840 --> 02:01.840
Three gunshots in the abdomen
and it's been a few hours.

02:02.200 --> 02:03.120
Where is he?

02:03.320 --> 02:05.560
I don't know how long
before I get him out.

02:05.640 --> 02:06.520
And listen,

02:07.600 --> 02:09.600
the police are tracking me down.

02:11.760 --> 02:13.080
Is it safe for them?

02:13.360 --> 02:15.880
They already know
and they agreed to their part.

02:16.400 --> 02:17.800
Yours would be ten million.

02:20.800 --> 02:22.960
I need abdominal laparotomy gear,

02:23.200 --> 02:26.240
a medical ventilator
and surgical equipment.

02:27.440 --> 02:28.400
Can you get it?

02:29.000 --> 02:29.960
I'll take care of it.

02:33.320 --> 02:35.920
WEDNESDAY
09:36 AM

02:41.800 --> 02:44.560
14 HOURS
SINCE THE SHOOTOUT

02:52.640 --> 02:54.720
Good morning. Inspector Murillo.

02:55.640 --> 02:59.320
I need the footage from the cameras
from October 23rd.

03:06.320 --> 03:07.600
-Here you go.
-Thank you.

03:08.120 --> 03:09.000
Bye.

03:22.800 --> 03:23.680
Thank you.

04:51.880 --> 04:53.720
Did you find out anything yet?

04:54.960 --> 04:56.240
I'm starting to draw

04:56.960 --> 04:58.800
the route he took to the cafeteria.

05:00.520 --> 05:02.520
Look, that narrows the area down

05:02.880 --> 05:04.760
to this triangle.

05:06.160 --> 05:07.720
If he went to Hanoi this way,

05:08.480 --> 05:10.640
His hideout is very close, in this area.

05:11.680 --> 05:13.120
I have to go out again, mom.

05:18.200 --> 05:20.840
The bulk of the calls were made
from this area.

05:21.320 --> 05:23.560
So the Professor must have
used these streets.

05:23.720 --> 05:26.880
Check the surveillance tapes
from this area.

05:27.400 --> 05:28.920
Get the judge to issue a warrant.

05:30.800 --> 05:31.920
This is headquarters...

06:53.040 --> 06:54.200
I told the kid.

06:58.600 --> 06:59.520
Told him what?

07:01.720 --> 07:02.600
What I did to you.

07:05.880 --> 07:08.320
That I abandoned you
at that roundabout in Martorell.

07:10.880 --> 07:12.560
I went back to that roundabout,

07:14.720 --> 07:15.600
because...

07:16.280 --> 07:18.480
I dreamed that you were
cleaning windshields

07:18.760 --> 07:19.960
at that stop light.

07:22.080 --> 07:23.080
I took the car

07:24.760 --> 07:25.640
and drove.

07:27.400 --> 07:28.880
Hours and hours,

07:30.240 --> 07:31.880
because I wanted to fix

07:32.640 --> 07:33.520
my mistake.

07:36.040 --> 07:36.920
Don't speak.

07:37.720 --> 07:39.480
-Rest.
-I showed your picture

07:41.200 --> 07:42.960
to everyone who passed by.

07:49.400 --> 07:50.280
And now...

07:51.160 --> 07:52.040
