07:55.160 --> 07:56.360
told me he hates me.

08:02.000 --> 08:02.840
Your son

08:03.720 --> 08:04.600
adores you.

08:07.200 --> 08:09.600
No matter what he says
in the heat of the moment.

08:10.000 --> 08:11.280
I know he doesn't hate you.

08:13.800 --> 08:14.960
Well, I deserve it.

08:17.800 --> 08:19.080
I took his mother from him.

08:19.360 --> 08:20.200
No.

08:22.120 --> 08:23.600
No, you did great.

08:26.400 --> 08:27.880
You have a wonderful son.

08:30.880 --> 08:31.760
Strong.

08:33.240 --> 08:34.120
Noble.

08:36.120 --> 08:37.040
And that...

08:39.720 --> 08:40.840
that's thanks to you.

08:42.720 --> 08:44.360
I did what I could, honey...

08:48.160 --> 08:49.840
He came out a little nuts, didn't he?

08:59.080 --> 08:59.960
I have never

09:00.680 --> 09:01.680
been as happy

09:03.560 --> 09:04.800
as the day I met you.

09:10.000 --> 09:11.960
If I have to go to some place now,

09:13.800 --> 09:15.160
I'd like it to be that one.

09:17.360 --> 09:18.480
The village festival.

09:23.000 --> 09:24.280
And dance with you,

09:25.120 --> 09:26.040
