09:30.760 --> 09:32.440
With the colorful lights.

09:35.760 --> 09:36.720
I love you.

09:37.720 --> 09:38.600
I'm sorry.

09:39.000 --> 09:39.880
Forgive me.

09:44.960 --> 09:45.800
Forgive me.

10:03.080 --> 10:03.920
I'm sorry.

10:05.920 --> 10:07.240
I'm sorry.

10:09.800 --> 10:10.920
I'm sorry.

10:18.520 --> 10:19.440
I'm so sorry.

