16:26.120 --> 16:27.880
You have to go back up, now.

16:28.400 --> 16:30.040
Do you understand? Look at me.

16:30.200 --> 16:31.760
If you don't go up now,

16:32.400 --> 16:34.440
you'll regret it for the rest
of your life.

16:34.600 --> 16:35.480
Go up.

16:36.960 --> 16:37.920
Go up.

16:41.200 --> 16:42.080
Hey!

16:42.200 --> 16:43.040
Let's go.

16:44.760 --> 16:45.600
Let's go.

16:47.200 --> 16:48.080
Let's go.

16:49.520 --> 16:50.440
Let's go.

16:51.480 --> 16:52.400
Let's go.

16:59.440 --> 17:00.480
Come on!

17:35.920 --> 17:37.080
I'm here, papa.

17:39.600 --> 17:42.680
Just hold a little longer
because we're going to make it.

17:43.240 --> 17:45.120
Right, Rio? We're digging like crazy.

17:45.280 --> 17:47.560
We already hear
the Serbs on the other side.

17:50.480 --> 17:51.400
Don't worry.

17:53.520 --> 17:54.440
Dad...

17:55.280 --> 17:56.240
-What?
-That...

17:59.000 --> 18:00.360
That thing I said about

18:01.760 --> 18:02.600
hating you...

18:06.400 --> 18:08.400
I could never feel that for you.

18:10.160 --> 18:11.600
I can't hate you, okay?

18:14.480 --> 18:16.120
It's okay. Don't worry.

18:16.200 --> 18:17.960
You did what you had to do with mom.

18:20.800 --> 18:22.160
But I can't hate you.

18:31.600 --> 18:32.520
Monica.

18:33.280 --> 18:34.120
Yes?

18:35.120 --> 18:37.400
I'll give you 300 million if you keep him.

18:39.640 --> 18:41.160
This guy's a headache.

18:43.760 --> 18:44.880
I brought him here,

18:46.600 --> 18:47.440
But...

18:48.000 --> 18:49.640
now I'm going on vacation.

18:50.040 --> 18:50.960
Of course I will.

18:51.800 --> 18:52.720
Take care of him.

19:01.400 --> 19:02.360
Gentlemen.

19:06.000 --> 19:07.400
I haven't introduced myself.

19:12.400 --> 19:13.400
Agustin Ramos.

19:16.800 --> 19:18.120
And it's been a pleasure.

19:31.000 --> 19:31.960
I love you.

19:35.280 --> 19:36.720
I love you too, papa.

19:37.600 --> 19:38.480
So much.

19:39.800 --> 19:41.200
And I'm not letting you go.

19:41.400 --> 19:43.640
Rio, bring all the explosives
we have left.

19:43.720 --> 19:45.480
I'm blowing up that tunnel.

19:46.480 --> 19:47.400
Don’t.

19:48.600 --> 19:49.960
If you blow the tunnel

19:51.160 --> 19:52.360
you'll bury us all.

19:53.880 --> 19:54.720
But papa...

19:58.320 --> 19:59.720
You have to carry on.

20:01.600 --> 20:02.560
And remember...

20:03.160 --> 20:05.120
-Remember what?
-"No rear-view mirrors".

20:07.480 --> 20:08.400
Alright.

20:10.000 --> 20:10.880
Alright.

20:12.800 --> 20:14.080
But I don't know if I can...

20:14.400 --> 20:15.320
I love you.

20:20.120 --> 20:21.080
I love you too.

20:22.760 --> 20:23.800
I love you too.

20:35.320 --> 20:37.360
It was for the absence of your lips

20:40.520 --> 20:42.560
That I cried for the first time

20:45.280 --> 20:46.840
And I cursed having met you

20:48.560 --> 20:51.600
For not being able to stop loving you

20:54.400 --> 20:56.840
You, my wife I wished to make

20:58.120 --> 20:59.840
And without love, I searched for luck

21:00.640 --> 21:03.200
I pulled out a gun

21:03.520 --> 21:07.080
And fate brought death

21:13.080 --> 21:16.760
Maria, my life, my love

21:17.440 --> 21:18.840
I promised

21:19.400 --> 21:21.320
That I'd return

21:21.760 --> 21:25.560
But I will not return

21:25.800 --> 21:29.760
I was caught by the police

21:30.040 --> 21:33.760
Maria, my life, my love

21:34.240 --> 21:35.680
I will not stop

21:36.040 --> 21:38.240
Loving you

21:38.320 --> 21:41.560
The hugs that I lost

21:42.440 --> 21:47.200
You will not see me again

22:23.800 --> 22:26.080
All the shops in the area
said the same.

22:26.160 --> 22:28.800
Inspector Murillo has seized footage

22:28.880 --> 22:30.760
crucial for the investigation.

22:30.960 --> 22:33.960
Indisputable evidence
that she's collaborating in the heist.

22:34.040 --> 22:35.880
Activate the intervention protocol.

22:36.720 --> 22:37.560
Immediately.

22:39.000 --> 22:40.360
Gather your best men.

22:41.120 --> 22:42.400
What about the hostages?

22:42.560 --> 22:44.800
And Alison Parker,
or the international protocol?

22:44.880 --> 22:46.240
What about public safety?

22:46.600 --> 22:49.040
Colonel, they have large caliber guns,

22:49.120 --> 22:51.040
entrances loaded with explosives.

22:51.120 --> 22:53.960
The hostages wear jumpsuits
and masks, like the thieves.

22:54.040 --> 22:55.600
Impossible to tell them apart.

22:55.720 --> 22:57.800
It will be a bloodbath and you know it.

22:58.800 --> 22:59.960
And what do you suggest?

23:01.120 --> 23:04.240
Let them get away,
holding hands with Inspector Murillo?

23:04.320 --> 23:06.880
Yes. Let them get out
and catch them outside.

23:09.920 --> 23:12.480
Do you know where
public safety has led us?

23:13.800 --> 23:14.960
You want me to tell you?

23:16.120 --> 23:17.760
To us being the laughing stock.

23:18.680 --> 23:21.320
Not only of Spain,
of the whole fucking world.

23:21.720 --> 23:24.640
The world's newscasts follow this story

23:24.720 --> 23:26.120
as if it were the World Cup.

23:26.720 --> 23:28.840
Do you want to be on TV
with the headline:

23:29.000 --> 23:32.520
"The idiots in the police
let an escaped prisoner re-enter

23:32.600 --> 23:35.520
the Royal Mint factory
riding a motorbike".

23:36.360 --> 23:37.920
A motorbike!

23:42.760 --> 23:44.600
Do you like being the goddamn foo?

23:44.760 --> 23:45.600
Excuse me...

23:46.000 --> 23:47.800
I didn't ask for your opinion.

23:48.000 --> 23:50.400
The government has given
the order to intervene.

23:50.480 --> 23:53.400
They have been in there for 125 hours,

23:53.520 --> 23:55.560
and if by chance they were to escape

23:55.640 --> 23:58.040
it would be a disgrace to this country.

23:58.160 --> 23:59.320
-Excuse me...
-What?

23:59.640 --> 24:02.160
The State Prosecutor's Office
issued an arrest warrant

24:02.240 --> 24:03.640
for Inspector Raquel Murillo.

24:04.400 --> 24:06.680
She is under search and arrest.

24:16.400 --> 24:17.320
Shall we close it?

24:21.480 --> 24:22.440
Just like that?

24:23.200 --> 24:24.120
We should...

24:25.320 --> 24:26.960
say a few words or something.

24:45.360 --> 24:47.160
Our Father who art in Heaven,

24:49.080 --> 24:50.880
hallowed be Thy name.

24:52.320 --> 24:54.720
Thy will be done on earth,
as it is in Heaven.

24:55.200 --> 24:56.520
Thy Kingdom come.

24:56.800 --> 24:57.680
What?

24:58.240 --> 24:59.400
You skipped a part.

24:59.720 --> 25:02.400
After "hallowed be Thy name"
comes "Thy Kingdom come."

25:02.480 --> 25:04.160
What the hell does that matter?

25:04.960 --> 25:06.200
If you're going to pray,

25:06.280 --> 25:07.280
do it right.

25:07.360 --> 25:10.800
You think God is checking
if you're saying it right?

25:18.000 --> 25:19.560
Give us this day our daily bread.

25:23.000 --> 25:24.240
And forgive us our debts,

25:25.560 --> 25:28.160
as we also have forgiven our debtors.

25:30.400 --> 25:32.040
And lead us not into temptation,

25:34.040 --> 25:35.320
but deliver us from evil.

25:36.440 --> 25:37.360
Amen.

25:51.400 --> 25:52.840
There are moments in life

25:53.440 --> 25:55.920
where you should be able
to have a remote control

25:56.800 --> 25:57.840
so you could stop it.

25:59.520 --> 26:01.320
Even if just for five minutes.

26:03.080 --> 26:06.000
But some things happen
with irreverent obscenity.

26:07.480 --> 26:09.400
And there's nothing you can do.

26:10.880 --> 26:11.800
On the one hand

26:12.680 --> 26:14.240
we had just buried Moscow.

26:16.120 --> 26:17.040
On the other,

26:17.720 --> 26:20.240
we were opening the path to our freedom.

