31:56.720 --> 31:59.000
Now we have to find Inspector Murillo

31:59.600 --> 32:01.320
and her little boyfriend.

32:01.640 --> 32:02.560
Lieutenant.

32:19.640 --> 32:21.240
Come on, go, go!

32:35.520 --> 32:36.640
-Squadron!
-Sir!

