34:23.360 --> 34:24.480
And there,

34:24.840 --> 34:27.880
you get to ask whoever the fuck you want
what he's wearing.

34:40.080 --> 34:40.960
Don't move.

34:41.920 --> 34:42.800
Don't move.

34:44.040 --> 34:45.080
Don't move!

35:00.600 --> 35:01.480
Don't move!

35:02.800 --> 35:03.720
Stay where you are!

35:40.640 --> 35:42.840
MOSCOW. AGUSTIN RAMOS
DOS HERMANAS. MAY 1, 1964

35:42.920 --> 35:44.360
He was born on Labor Day.

35:47.320 --> 35:50.240
On every birthday since he started
working at the mine he said

35:51.240 --> 35:53.400
all the arrangements
were made for his party.

35:53.720 --> 35:54.560
A good picket.

35:55.800 --> 35:57.640
And the rubber bullets were his gifts.

36:01.000 --> 36:02.520
This year it was real bullets.

36:07.800 --> 36:09.760
I guess if you're born on the wrong side,

36:11.040 --> 36:12.320
you die on the wrong side.

36:15.800 --> 36:16.760
What's your name?

36:17.760 --> 36:20.080
-No, Monica.
-I need to know your name.

36:20.800 --> 36:22.760
Because I'm leaving here with you.

36:24.160 --> 36:27.560
Through the back door,
the tunnel, or holding a machine gun.

36:29.120 --> 36:30.800
But I don't want to be away from you.

36:32.200 --> 36:33.680
And if I have to learn to shoot,

36:33.800 --> 36:34.640
I will.

36:36.520 --> 36:37.440
Besides...

36:39.080 --> 36:40.080
this child...

36:41.080 --> 36:42.880
this child is going to need a father.

36:47.000 --> 36:48.360
Come on, tell me your name.

36:54.560 --> 36:55.760
Ricardo.

37:13.640 --> 37:16.600
This is the Underground Unit,
making our way down the sewers.

37:18.960 --> 37:20.760
-What's that noise?
-Stay still.

37:23.440 --> 37:26.080
It’s the metro. Line 6.
It's right above us.

37:26.520 --> 37:27.520
Proceeding.

37:32.240 --> 37:34.440
Come on, people! Keep it up!

37:34.920 --> 37:38.800
Let's make sure the magic lasts
until the very end!

37:42.480 --> 37:45.880
In there, we'll have satellite
radio and video signal

37:45.960 --> 37:48.160
in order to avoid frequency jammers.

37:49.200 --> 37:50.120
The bomb squad

37:50.640 --> 37:54.720
will open a gap in the cargo door.
300 grams of thermite explosive.

37:54.800 --> 37:56.480
You know what that means.

37:57.000 --> 37:58.120
So Lobo, Ruiz,

37:59.040 --> 38:01.360
you'll provide cover fire, if necessary.

38:01.760 --> 38:05.160
The rest of us will enter in line,
no one stays behind.

38:05.360 --> 38:07.160
Come on, come on, come on!

38:07.400 --> 38:08.240
Gentlemen,

38:08.720 --> 38:10.720
there's going to be a ruckus in there,

38:11.240 --> 38:13.080
so we'll have to be united.

38:13.400 --> 38:14.240
Together!

38:15.280 --> 38:16.120
Understood?

38:16.240 --> 38:17.320
Yes, sir!

38:31.440 --> 38:32.720
The only instructions

38:33.200 --> 38:35.960
are not to open fire if they wear a mask.

38:36.920 --> 38:40.920
Of course, we will open fire
in response to anyone shooting at us.

38:42.200 --> 38:43.600
The only instructions

38:44.120 --> 38:47.400
are that there's no order for any of them
to come out alive.

38:48.000 --> 38:48.880
Is that clear?

38:58.280 --> 38:59.240
Is that clear?

38:59.320 --> 39:00.520
Yes, sir!

39:17.360 --> 39:19.400
We're ready, so let's go get them!

39:19.480 --> 39:20.520
Go, go, go!

39:44.600 --> 39:45.480
Rio,

39:46.000 --> 39:47.720
-Rio, are you there?
-Yes, Professor.

39:47.800 --> 39:51.000
-I encrypted the frequency.
-How long can it take to decode it?

39:51.080 --> 39:51.920
Two hours.

39:53.400 --> 39:54.360
Perfect.

39:54.440 --> 39:55.960
Set the explosive charges.

39:56.040 --> 39:57.520
Pass the intercom to Berlin.

39:57.600 --> 39:58.480
Right away.

39:59.680 --> 40:00.560
Hey.

40:02.120 --> 40:03.080
Come, please.

40:12.000 --> 40:12.920
What's the matter?

40:13.000 --> 40:14.160
I don't feel well.

40:15.560 --> 40:16.400
What's wrong?

40:17.720 --> 40:18.960
I feel pain in my chest.

40:19.040 --> 40:21.640
May be an anxiety attack.
Do you want a tranquilizer?

41:02.040 --> 41:05.040
It would have been easier for me too
if none of this had happened.

41:08.720 --> 41:09.800
It was the only

41:10.880 --> 41:13.160
actual crack
in an otherwise perfect plan.

41:13.240 --> 41:15.720
A plan no longer perfect. You know why?

41:18.120 --> 41:19.960
Because even if this all goes well...

41:22.800 --> 41:24.720
Even if it all goes well, I'll be...

41:25.880 --> 41:27.080
I'll be fucked.

41:30.400 --> 41:32.160
Because I won't ever see you again.

41:34.400 --> 41:36.720
You think it was in my plans
to fall in love

41:36.800 --> 41:38.160
with the inspector?

41:38.240 --> 41:39.480
I don't want to hear more.

41:43.760 --> 41:44.880
You don't want to hear?

41:47.520 --> 41:49.160
Why don’t you want to hear, Raquel?

41:52.600 --> 41:54.000
Because I'm a bad guy?

41:57.400 --> 42:00.080
You've been taught
to see good and bad guys.

42:01.000 --> 42:04.720
But what we're doing
is okay to you when other people do it.

42:05.160 --> 42:09.280
In the year 2011,
the European Central Bank made 171

42:10.880 --> 42:12.480
billion euros out of nowhere.

42:14.760 --> 42:16.160
Just like we're doing.

42:17.600 --> 42:18.880
Only bigger.

42:19.360 --> 42:22.600
185 billion in 2012.

42:22.680 --> 42:25.720
145 billion euros in the 2013.

42:25.840 --> 42:27.960
Do you know where all that money went?

42:31.280 --> 42:32.320
To the banks.

42:33.000 --> 42:34.520
Directly from the factory

42:36.000 --> 42:37.400
to the pockets of the rich.

42:40.160 --> 42:41.360
Did anyone call

42:42.720 --> 42:44.800
the European Central Bank a thief?

42:47.480 --> 42:48.400
No.

42:49.520 --> 42:50.880
"Liquidity injections",

42:50.960 --> 42:52.000
they called it.

42:53.000 --> 42:54.960
And they pulled it out of nowhere, Raquel.

42:55.120 --> 42:56.040
Out of nowhere.

43:05.240 --> 43:06.200
What's this?

43:06.680 --> 43:08.760
This is nothing, Raquel. Paper.

43:10.320 --> 43:11.760
It's paper, you see?

43:13.720 --> 43:14.640
It's paper.

43:18.160 --> 43:20.120
I'm making a liquidity injection,

43:22.000 --> 43:23.160
but not for the banks.

43:23.800 --> 43:24.880
I'm doing it here,

43:25.600 --> 43:26.840
in the real economy.

43:27.200 --> 43:28.440
With this group of...

43:29.000 --> 43:31.160
of losers, which is what we are, Raquel.

43:35.720 --> 43:37.120
To get away from it all.

43:41.000 --> 43:42.480
Don't you want to get away?

43:54.680 --> 43:56.280
Angel is calling you.

43:56.960 --> 43:58.960
Does this mean he woke up?

44:01.120 --> 44:02.800
If he's awake, they're going to...

44:02.880 --> 44:05.240
He'll talk and they will be here
in five minutes.

44:06.560 --> 44:07.400
Okay,

44:07.480 --> 44:08.720
I'm going to answer it.

44:09.160 --> 44:12.160
And you'll speak.
But no nonsense, please.

44:12.240 --> 44:13.120
Please.

44:13.640 --> 44:14.760
You'll answer it

44:15.440 --> 44:16.880
and you're going to verify

44:17.520 --> 44:18.880
if he's awake, okay?

44:20.480 --> 44:21.360
Please.

44:22.600 --> 44:23.480
Please.

44:24.240 --> 44:26.240
No, no! Don't answer it.

44:27.240 --> 44:28.680
Don't answer it.

44:30.720 --> 44:31.920
My phone is tapped.

44:36.400 --> 44:37.880
Do you have another one?

44:51.160 --> 44:52.040
Who is it?

44:52.280 --> 44:53.280
Raquel.

44:53.360 --> 44:54.400
Raquel Murillo.

44:55.960 --> 44:57.040
Angel woke up.

44:57.720 --> 45:00.400
He didn't want us to call anyone
before he talked to you.

45:00.720 --> 45:01.720
I'll put him on.

45:07.360 --> 45:08.240
Raquel,

45:14.120 --> 45:15.000
how are you?

45:21.000 --> 45:21.880
Don't worry,

45:22.240 --> 45:23.280
come on.

45:25.360 --> 45:26.320
Take it easy.

45:27.720 --> 45:28.720
Come on, Raquel.

45:29.880 --> 45:31.520
-How are you?
-Me?

45:32.520 --> 45:34.960
So high I can't even feel my ass.

45:41.320 --> 45:42.440
Listen,

45:43.600 --> 45:45.440
I saw on the TV that you've...

45:46.160 --> 45:48.360
you've been replaced in the investigation.

45:49.480 --> 45:50.360
Yes.

45:52.480 --> 45:54.680
Don't tell anyone I woke up, okay?

45:57.000 --> 45:58.720
I need you to come see me first.

46:01.000 --> 46:02.000
Okay.

46:08.280 --> 46:11.200
Colonel, we've picked up a phone call
to Murillo's number.

46:11.600 --> 46:13.280
But there was no communication.

46:13.360 --> 46:15.360
Locate the call immediately.

46:15.440 --> 46:17.160
Get the owner and the antenna.

46:17.240 --> 46:18.120
Now.

46:20.280 --> 46:22.080
You have to let me go talk to Angel.

46:23.720 --> 46:27.800
If I don't go, in 15 minutes
he'll tell the police where you are.

46:28.600 --> 46:29.720
And I can stop him.

46:30.320 --> 46:32.080
-It's your only chance...
-Please.

46:32.160 --> 46:35.120
It's about your perfect plan
not falling apart.

46:35.200 --> 46:36.720
Please, let me think.

46:36.800 --> 46:38.320
There's nothing to think about.

46:38.560 --> 46:39.440
Sergio.

46:56.800 --> 46:57.720
I'm with you.

46:59.240 --> 47:02.200
A minute ago you were screaming
and biting me like an animal.

47:06.440 --> 47:07.480
Can I trust you?

47:08.200 --> 47:09.040
Come.

47:09.800 --> 47:10.680
Come closer.

